videos.description: Emmett Naar outlets a pass to Jock Landale in transition and he throws down the two-handed jam.
videos.headline: Landale's hustle leads to slam for Saint Mary's

videos.description: Jock Landale makes a nice dish to Evan Fitzner who knocks down the corner 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Saint Mary's hitting on all cylinders

videos.description: Jock Landale fakes the hand-off then drives for the two-handed flush.
videos.headline: Landale showing his versatility

videos.description: Cullen Neal makes a lob pass to Jordan Hunter who throws it down hard for the two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Saint Mary's puts exclamation point on game
